message.body: Hey ivan, if youre still around tonight would you like to play at the canaret party?
Its an after party for leon redbone, its at signal kitchen at 1030
Oh man I'd love to, but my singing voice is still not very there. If that changes today, ill letcha know... Is there a cover to get in?
Its 12$, i got someone for tonight but if youre here with more singing juice tomorrow youre still welcome to play , n get in free
Gotcha! I think that might work; let's pencil it in...?
